<html lang='fr' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml' xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width,initial-scale=1' />
    <meta name='x-apple-disable-message-reformatting' />
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Homemade+Apple&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap' rel='stylesheet' />
    <title>Ta sortie du {{date}}</title>

    <style>
      table, td, div, h1, p { font-family: Jost, Arial, sans-serif; } @media screen and (max-width: 530px) { .unsub { display: block; padding: 8px;
      margin-top: 14px; border-radius: 6px; background-color: #f2e8dc; text-decoration: none !important; } .col-lge { max-width: 100% !important; } }
      @media screen and (min-width: 531px) { .col-sml { max-width: 27% !important; } .col-lge { max-width: 73% !important; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style='margin: 0; padding: 0; word-spacing: normal'>
    <div
      role='article'
      aria-roledescription='email'
      lang='fr'
      style='
        text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        background-color: #001f36;
        background-position: center;
        padding: 0 0 40px 0;
      '
    >
      <table role='presentation' style='width: 100%; border: none; border-spacing: 0'>
        <tr>
          <td align='center' style='padding: 0'>
            <table
              role='presentation'
              style='
                width: 94%;
                max-width: 600px;
                border: none;
                border-spacing: 0;
                text-align: left;
                font-family: Jost, Arial, sans-serif;
                font-size: 17px;
                line-height: 22px;
                color: #001f36;
                padding-bottom: 40px;
              '
            >
              <tr>
                <td style='padding: 40px 30px 30px 30px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px'>
                  <a href='https://www.larga2.fr' style='text-decoration: none'>
                    <img
                      src='https://i.ibb.co/vJZ9QKk/logo512.png'
                      style='
                        width: 20%;
                        /* max-width: 600px;
                        border: none;
                        border-spacing: 0;
                        text-align: left;
                        font-family: Jost, Arial, sans-serif;
                        font-size: 17px;
                        line-height: 22px;
                        color: #001f36;
                        padding-bottom: 40px; */
                      '
                    />
                  </a>
                </td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td style='padding: 30px; background-color: #f2e8dc'>
                  <p style='margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.02em'>Coucou Denis,</p>
                  <p style='margin: 0'>Voici le récap de la sortie :</p>

                  <ul style='list-style: none'>
                    <li>📅 Date : {{date}}</li>
                    <li>👥 Participants : {{counter}}</li>
                    <li>👤 Contact 1 : {{firstname}} {{lastname}} | 📞 {{phone}} | ✉️ {{email}}. Accompagnants : Jean Martin</li>

                    <li>📞 Contact 2 : {{firstname}} {{lastname}} / {{phone}}</li>
                    <li>📞 Contact 3 : {{firstname}} {{lastname}} / {{phone}}</li>
                    <li>📞 Contact 4 : {{firstname}} {{lastname}} / {{phone}}</li>
                  </ul>

                  <p>
                    Le nombre total de participants sur cette journée s'élève à
                    <strong>{{totalpax}}</strong>.
                  </p>

                  <p style='margin: 0; color: red'>VEUX TU INSERER D'AUTRES INFOS ?!</p>

                  <p>Liens utiles:</p>
                  <ul style='list-style: none'>
                    <li>
                      🌤️
                      <a style='color: #001f36' href='https://www.windy.com/43.332/5.152?42.870,5.153,8'>Coup d'oeil météo (Windy)</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      ✉️
                      <a style='color: #001f36' href='mailto: {{emails}}'>Leur envoyer un mail groupé</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      📱
                      <a style='color: #001f36' href='mailto: {{emails}}'>Leur envoyer un sms groupé</a>
                    </li>
                  </ul>

                  <p>Belle sortie à toi et ton équipage ! ✨⛵️</p>
                  <p>Amicalement,</p>
                  <p>Léa</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>